data.description: Looking for a place to roam? Want to live close to the lake and have enough room to park your boat? Come and check this house now!  This beautifully updated 5 bedrooms 3 baths home in desirable Lakewood estates has wood laminate floors throughout and no carpet to worry about! It features great lay out with Master Bedroom, Secondary Bedroom and two bathrooms downstairs. Multipurpose Secondary  Bedroom can be used as a Guest suite or a Study and is perfect for someone who works from home. Outstanding Kitchen has plenty of tall cabinets, breakfast bar, granite countertops, stainless steel  gas range and huge pantry. It opens to a large Family Room with stone fireplace that is a perfect place to enjoy during cool winter nights; generous Loft and three spacious Secondary Bedrooms upstairs create a perfect arrangement for the family and guests. Master Retreat with luxurious bathroom features garden tub, separate shower and granite his and her vanities. Adjacent Utility Room has two storage closets and room for freezer or folding table. And if you like outdoor activity you will be pleased with private Backyard that backs to a wooded park with walking trails and is maintained by US Army Corps of Engineers. And for those who love to entertain there is a large patio to host barbecue parties and plenty of room for your boat to park! Great place to call Home!
